  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/c7faabc4f344eab1ba3b6289bd95cb11.avif?t=1718795772\" width=484 height=145 /></span><br><br><strong>\"Fable of Sand Paws\" combines exploration, puzzles and a little sokoban, in the game you will have to explore 3D dioramas, in search of the best way to collect the treasures scattered around the scenario. Move the camera around the dioramas to find secret passages and hidden areas, send the cat Sand Paws to explore these locations, and find out how to reach the treasures!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/18b56b31b2bd321ce46c29bb71020629.poster.avif?t=1718795772\" width=640 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/18b56b31b2bd321ce46c29bb71020629.webm?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/18b56b31b2bd321ce46c29bb71020629.mp4?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Throughout the game, you'll be able to move platforms and different blocks to create new accesses and paths to the treasures. The movement of the Sand Paws cat is done through point and click mechanics, so it will always look for the best way to get to the point where you aim. It collects the treasures automatically, as soon as it reaches it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/5e4f03ac38ea5bdb7f301544e0d343b7.poster.avif?t=1718795772\" width=640 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/5e4f03ac38ea5bdb7f301544e0d343b7.webm?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/5e4f03ac38ea5bdb7f301544e0d343b7.mp4?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Collect keys to unlock doors that are closing off certain area.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/10b6ad1b937dcaa8f6e772b6a951b89e.poster.avif?t=1718795772\" width=640 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/10b6ad1b937dcaa8f6e772b6a951b89e.webm?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/10b6ad1b937dcaa8f6e772b6a951b89e.mp4?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Hit boxes to clear paths, solve puzzles or use them to hold down buttons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/2951f6bd859903c3216873465fa4e992.poster.avif?t=1718795772\" width=640 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/2951f6bd859903c3216873465fa4e992.webm?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/2951f6bd859903c3216873465fa4e992.mp4?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 30+ challenging scenarios<br></li><li>3 different worlds<br></li><li>Bite-sized gameplay. Levels take ~1-4 minutes each.<br></li><li>Original soundtrack<br></li><li>Gameplay that mixes exploration with puzzles<br></li><li>Cute kittens</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/c7faabc4f344eab1ba3b6289bd95cb11.avif?t=1718795772\" width=484 height=145 /></span><br><br><strong>\"Fable of Sand Paws\" combines exploration, puzzles and a little sokoban, in the game you will have to explore 3D dioramas, in search of the best way to collect the treasures scattered around the scenario. Move the camera around the dioramas to find secret passages and hidden areas, send the cat Sand Paws to explore these locations, and find out how to reach the treasures!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/18b56b31b2bd321ce46c29bb71020629.poster.avif?t=1718795772\" width=640 height=318 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/18b56b31b2bd321ce46c29bb71020629.webm?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/18b56b31b2bd321ce46c29bb71020629.mp4?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Throughout the game, you'll be able to move platforms and different blocks to create new accesses and paths to the treasures. The movement of the Sand Paws cat is done through point and click mechanics, so it will always look for the best way to get to the point where you aim. It collects the treasures automatically, as soon as it reaches it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/5e4f03ac38ea5bdb7f301544e0d343b7.poster.avif?t=1718795772\" width=640 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/5e4f03ac38ea5bdb7f301544e0d343b7.webm?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/5e4f03ac38ea5bdb7f301544e0d343b7.mp4?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Collect keys to unlock doors that are closing off certain area.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/10b6ad1b937dcaa8f6e772b6a951b89e.poster.avif?t=1718795772\" width=640 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/10b6ad1b937dcaa8f6e772b6a951b89e.webm?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/10b6ad1b937dcaa8f6e772b6a951b89e.mp4?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Hit boxes to clear paths, solve puzzles or use them to hold down buttons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/2951f6bd859903c3216873465fa4e992.poster.avif?t=1718795772\" width=640 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/2951f6bd859903c3216873465fa4e992.webm?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948690/extras/2951f6bd859903c3216873465fa4e992.mp4?t=1718795772\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>More than 30+ challenging scenarios<br></li><li>3 different worlds<br></li><li>Bite-sized gameplay. Levels take ~1-4 minutes each.<br></li><li>Original soundtrack<br></li><li>Gameplay that mixes exploration with puzzles<br></li><li>Cute kittens</li></ul>",
